sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import moment from 'moment'; const ProjectItem = ({ id, name, start_date, end_date, assigned_to, type, payment_received, payment_date}) => { return ( {id} {name} {/* {number} */} {moment(start_date).format('DD/MM/YYYY')} {moment(end_date).format('DD/MM/YYYY')} {assigned_to} {type} {payment_received} {moment(payment_date).format('DD/MM/YYYY')} Edit ); } export default ProjectItem;
